             was indicted for <rs id="t18240916-190-off1034" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240916-190-off1034" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240916-190-off1034" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240916-190-cd1035" type="crimeDate">20th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-190-off1034 t18240916-190-cd1035"></join>, a gelding, value 25 l.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240916-190-victim1608" type="victimName">
                     Sharrard 
                     Hart
                  <interp inst="t18240916-190-victim1608" type="surname" value="Hart"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240916-190-victim1608" type="given" value="Sharrard"></interp>
